HEADWORD: Aint
<hw>Ain't</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <def>A contraction for <xex>are not</xex>
and <xex>am not</xex>; also used for <xex>is not</xex>. <mark>[Colloq.
or illiterate speech]</mark>. See <er>An't</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>aioli</ent>⟦br⟧
